Harvey Associates, Inc.












After-Market Auto Parts  



















 


Ken Harvey

Ken Harvey has been in the automotive aftermarket for his entire career with the exception of a brief stint with Xerox Corporation after receiving his MBA from Tuck Business School.  He owned and operated E.B. Harvey and Associates and Sterling ompany of New England as a manufacturers rep and automotive warehouse distributor with his partner Chip Harvey until 1999.  Ken has extensive experience at every level of the aftermarket, and is currently a New England Show Committee member and trustee. Ken is semi-retired and works with us in specific areas where his long time relationships in the industry are a great asset.









